reviews.reviewText: Performs as promised. The pump feature with the included hose eliminates the need to be emptying the bucket. Keeps the space at the desired humidity level.

reviews.name: Hisense Energy Star 70 Pt 2-Speed Dehumidifier with Built-In Pump, DH-70KP1SDLE
reviews.reviewText: Delivered to my door. Easy to set up and the best part NO MORE having to empty the bucket. PS it comes with it's own hose. It started producing dryer air right away.
reviews.title: Good value and good performance.

reviews.name: Hisense Energy Star 70 Pt 2-Speed Dehumidifier with Built-In Pump, DH-70KP1SDLE
reviews.reviewText: Florida, temperature 74 deg with 95% humidity outside. The dehumidifier pulls down the indoor humidity to 55% without lowering the house temperature. The pump works well. Noise, what can you do, but close doors. We are very pleased with our purchase.
reviews.title: Dryes the the house to 55% quicky

reviews.name: Hisense Energy Star 70 Pt 2-Speed Dehumidifier with Built-In Pump, DH-70KP1SDLE
reviews.reviewText: Did not work out of the box. Customer service said the compressor was probably bad and to return it to Walmart which I did. Money was returned without issue. Purchased another from a different maker (Frigidaire) and have been pleased so far.
reviews.title: returned
